Object Oriented Programing final project.
Tanks game created from scratch. 
.Exe available for download and play if you don't care about the code.

wasd to move
mouse click to shoot

Most everything is encapulated in objects.
Levels are randomly generated at the start of booting. 
Each level is scaled up in difficultly the further you progress.
Enemy Ai: targets the nearest tank to it, attempts to avoid being shot while also shooting others
all tanks are destroyed when killed.
When any tank kills another tank it receives an upgrade to an inherited class type. (Tracking bullets)
Walls are generated randomly around the screen. 
Wall Collision enabled for tanks and bullets.
get through 10 levels to win.

